data.description: Beautiful move in ready condo on the intercostal waterway in Daytona Beach.  Recently refreshed with new flooring, new paint, ceilings resurfaced, new ceiling fans and light fixtures.  The kitchen has granite countertops and newer appliances.  An excellent view of the river and the new Orange Avenue bridge which was just recently constructed from the living room and master bedroom.  Master bedroom also features a walk-in closet.  Large screened patio measures 25 feet long and 5 feet wide.  Condo has a private laundry and storage room across the hall from the front door to the unit.  The condo complex has covered parking, beautifully maintained grounds, inground pool and a dock.There are fireworks directly over the river after Friday night Daytona Tortugas games.
